  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "A contrastive loss then aligns both feature vectors in the shared embedding space.",
    "For HistoCLIP we use the same loss as for CLIP 47.",
    "For HistoSigLIP, we use the loss proposed in SigLIP 48.",
    "In pursuit of improving performance and avoiding training instabilities, we freeze the vision encoder during training.",
    "This technique is called locked-image text tuning 49)."
  ],
